title: House Fancy
description: Nicholas Withers tours the fanciest homes in hopes of crowning a House Fancy Prince of the Year.
quote: It’s like I’ve died and gone to fancy heaven!
altHero: Nicholas Withers, a fish with a big grin, blonde hair, and green sweater
alt1: Nicholas speaks with Squilliam Fancyson, a unibrowed octopus in a smoking jacket.
alt2: a grand hallway with columns, sculptures, and chandeliers
alt3: a fancy golden toilet with a spotlight on it
alt4: a lush garden with pink grotto and statues of seahorses
